title: Bonney Lake Rental
posting_body: ["Here's everything you've wished for! 5 bed, 3.5 bath home on greenbelt.", 'Main floor boasts large kitchen w/ island that opens to great room, bedroom and full bath and lots of windows overlooking the private back yard w/ sprinkler system and huge covered patio w/ gas line for BBQ.', 'Upstairs is the Master Suite + 3 beds (one is large enough to be a bonus room instead), main bath and laundry Other features include AC, all new carpet, oversized 2 car garage and all appliances stay!', "Don't let this one get away!", 'Get approved quickly so you can live in this beautiful home.', 'In order to qualify for the Rent To Own Program:', '• You must have at least $85,000 in Combined Gross Household Income', '•', 'A minimum FICO score of 620', '• No evictions in the past 3 years', '• Takes 5-6 weeks from start to finish', 'We work with previous bankruptcies, foreclosures and short sales!', 'There is a 1 time $75 application fee, which is good for the whole household, and for any of our qualifying houses!', 'You must be pre-approved to view any available properties.', 'Pet Friendly!', 'Up to 3 cats/dogs OKAY!', '(Due to extreme insurance liability, we cannot allow Dobermans, Pitbulls, Rottweilers or Mastiffs)', 'Contact me today for more information and details about the program!', "The home in the picture is an example of what you could get, it's not this home in particular.", 'Kristin Hood', 'Keller Williams Lake Tapps']
